Save and restore FPSCR register in ARM trusted&lt;-&gt;untrusted context switch

Save the untrusted code's state of FPSCR and restore the trusted
code's FPSCR when switching in from untrusted code.  Restore the
untrusted code's state of FPSCR when switching out to untrusted code.

